  <entry>
    <id>https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/137.0/releasenotes/</id>
    <title type="html">Thunderbird 137.0</title>
    <author>
      <name>Thunderbird</name>
      <uri>https://www.thunderbird.net</uri>
    </author>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/137.0/releasenotes/"/>
    <updated>2025-04-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <published>2025-04-01T00:00:00+00:00</published>

    <content type="html"><![CDATA[
      

  
  

  
    

    
      
        
        

        
          <h3>Changed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>File names are now used when storing mail folders (Windows only).</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Disable Linux system tray icon until it gains functionality</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        
          </ul>
        

        
          <h3>Fixed</h3>
        

        
        
          <ul>
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>In-app notifications did not display correctly in high contrast mode.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Repair folder did not fix mbox files produced on MacOS before Thunderbird 1.0.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Edit menu entries missing when group header selected in "Grouped by sort" view.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>IMAP folder "Undelete" performed "Delete" when mixed messages were selected.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>In RSS feeds, the space bar did not scroll the message like it did in emails.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Slow performance opening an .eml file in a profile with many folders.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Threaded search view was not updated correctly when sorted by date received.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Line spacing changed unexpectedly in the message list with the default font size.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Saved message list selection was discarded when user made a new selection.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Replying from local or unified folders failed when the message pane was hidden.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Message security panel strings were used in the wrong places.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Importing an OpenPGP public key with whitespace failed.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Unable to open attached signed OpenPGP .eml message.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Right-clicking "Decrypt and Save As..." on an attachment file failed.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Searching during shutdown could cause crash.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Failed news message sending could close the compose window unexpectedly.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Having a corrupt address book database prevented sending mail.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Forwarding messages as attachments could use the wrong MIME type.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Two-factor auth via text or email did not work with Office 365 using Oauth2.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Account settings menu could be loaded twice.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>No gap existed between Back and Forward buttons in the Feed Account Wizard dialog.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Thunderbird could crash when importing mail</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Unable to auto-discover Address Book on Radicale server.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Mark-Of-The-Web was not applied to attachments saved via drag and drop.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Some messages could not be scrolled due to hidden overflows in inline styles.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Clicking a 'mid:' link could clear the thread pane and cause errors.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Performance regressed when moving/copying messages on Windows.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Automatic compact did not attempt to compact all folders when error encountered.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Slow performance when moving bulk messages from IMAP to local.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Crossposting news article was not possible if newsgroups on different servers.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>IRC channel was not visible after restart.</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

